	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Gamegear emulators use the 2D-Mode hardware to display all the graphics, so it never has to run any code to render each pixel.
<br />
<br />SNES also uses the 2D hardware, but a SNES is more demanding to emulate.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


